'''Alfred Dreier''' (20 January 1940 â€“ 16 February 2011) was a [[German people|German]] jurist and local politician from the [[Christian Social Union of Bavaria]]. He occupied some posts including Minister of Culture of Bavaria from 1986 to 1987.<ref>{{cite news|title=Trauer um Alfred Dreier (71): Vize-Landrat a. D. stirbt an Krebs|url=http://www.merkur-online.de/lokales/erding/trauer-alfred-dreier-71-vize-landrat-stirbt-krebs-1126330.html|accessdate=30 April 2014|date=16 February 2011}}</ref>

==Honours==
*1995: [[Order of Merit of the Federal Republic of Germany]]
*1998: Medal for outstanding services to the local government

